title: DP-33 Simone Devon Devonshire Productions
description:
Simone Devon in a Devonshire Production video.  This 70 minute video contains Simone being restrained in various positions by Bryan Davis.  Ties include an inverted suspension, a standing strappado, a kneeling strappado and within a rope web wall. 

For hood enthusiasts, Simone's head is always covered.

Preview Pic: http://img245.imagevenue.com/img.php?image=60607_DP33_123_408lo.jpg

As with all Devonshire videos, there is on-screen tying  and all models are covered in some fashion on the bottom.

Warning: Due to a video transfer issue, static/distortion appears at the bottom of the screen throughout (visible in preview pic)
